>\n</div>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='two-column cf'>\n<div class='column-main'>\n<div class='column-main-inner'>\n<div class='stream-post-wrapper' id='stream-post-wrapper-24456'>\n<div class='stream-post-header cf'>\n<div class='stream-post-author'>\n<div class='stream-post-author-avatar'>\n<img onerror=\"this.src = &quot;https://wantedly-assets.wantedly.com/static/avatar/default_avatar_square_blue.png&quot;;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://d2v9k5u4v94ulw.cloudfront.net/small_light(dw=80,dh=80,da=l,ds=s,cw=80,ch=80,cc=FFFFFF)/assets/images/398567/original/3c25662e-4530-4cd6-9092-bab45230b405?1525169080\" />\n</div>\n<div class='stream-post-author-name no-title'>\n<p><a href=\"/companies/ca-wise\">株式会社CA Wise</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='stream-post-meta'>\n<div class='stream-post-date'>\n<div class='fa fa-clock-o'></div>\n2016/05/12\n<a class=\"stream-post-link-detail\" href=\"https://www.wantedly.com/companies/ca-wise/posts/24456\"><div class='fa fa-link'></div>\n</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='stream-post-content'>\n<div class='stream-post-content-body'><p>【リリース祝いやりました】</p>\n\n<p>システム的な分単位のアクセス状況から、売り上げ数値・対目標の達成状況などを可視化させたレポートツールのお祝いでした。これまで「やりたい」と思っても、足元の開発に追われて結果的にできていなかったことを入社から爆速で開発してくれました。担当エンジニアのdaichiからの開発に込められた想いが印象的でした。リリースおめでとう！</p>\n\n<p>前回、駄菓子に偏りがあったためか消化状況がいまいちだったので、今回は社内からアンケートをとって駄菓子を選定。リリースを重ねて駄菓子が増える。もう少し続けてみたいと思います。\n</p></div>\n<div class='stream-post-content-image'>\n<img src=\"https://d2v9k5u4v94ulw.cloudfront.net/small_light(dw=640,dh=640,da=l,ds=n,cc=FFFFFF)/assets/images/383726/original/e97470ae-7199-4b18-aa76-ae90fa5ab91a.jpeg?1463052479\" />\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='stream-post-footer cf'>\n<div class='stream-post-footer-left'>\n<div class='stream-post-like-container' id='stream-post-like-container-24456'>\n<span>\n<a class='stream-post-like need-to-signin' data-ref='company_post_like' href='#'>\nいいね！\n</a>\n</span>\n<div class='stream-post-like-count'>\n<i class='liked fa fa-heart animate__animated animate__bounceIn' style='display: none;'></i>\n<i class='unliked fa fa-heart-o' style=''></i>\n<div class='count'>1</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='stream-post-footer-right'>\n<div class='stream-post-share-container'>\n<a class='facebook share-facebook' data-url='https://www.wantedly.com/companies/ca-wise/posts/24456'>\n<i class='fa fa-facebook-square'></i>\nシェアする\n</a>\n<a class='twitter share-twitter' data-text='【リリース祝いやりました】システム的な分単位のアクセス状況から、売り上げ数値・対目標の達成状況... 株式会社CA Wise' data-url='https://www.wantedly.com/companies/ca-wise/posts/24456'>\n<i class='fa fa-twitter-square'></i>\nツイートする\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<a href=\"/companies/ca-wise\"><div class='fa fa-chevron-circle-left'></div>\n株式会社CA Wiseの投稿をもっとみる\n</a></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"/stories\"><div class='fa fa-chevron-circle-left'></div>\nストーリー\n</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='company-column-side'>\n<div class='column-side-inner'>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n        </div>\n          <p id=\"back-top\">\n            <a href=\"#top\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://wantedly-assets.wantedly.com/static/legacy/page-top-icon.png\" /></a>\n          </p>\n      </div>\n\n      \n\n          <div data-react-component-props='{&quot;app_env&quot;:&quot;production&quot;,&quot;locale&quot;:&quot;ja&quot;,&quot;country&quot;:&quot;JP&quot;,&quot;is_logged_in&quot;:false,&quot;is_utm_track_available&quot;:true,&quot;is_country_changeable&quot;:false,&quot;is_locale_changeable&quot;:false,&quot;is_company_info_visible&quot;:false,&quot;app_download_links&quot;:{&quot;visit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;student&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;people&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;company_page_info&quot;:null}' data-react-component='GlobalFooterContainer'></div>\n\n    </div>\n    <div data-locale='ja' data-user-avatar-url='https://wantedly-assets.wantedly.com/static/avatar/default_avatar_square_blue.png' id='global-civic-profile-modal'></div>\n\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n    \n    \n    <div